    "text": [
        "Dear Ann and Mike,",
        "I hope you are fine and this autumn weather doesn\u2019t have an influence on your moods. I\u2019m writing this letter to say a lot of thanks to you for allowing me to stay at your house during my training course in Dubai.",
        "The week I've spent in your house was one of the most enjoyable times in my life. You're such a lovely couple, so wish you to be happy together and hope your wedding party don't be shift anymore, neither because of a Covid pandemic nor because of any other reasons. I want to express special gratitude for the farewell dinner, which you arranged for me. It was a really good surprise for me. I'll remember it for my whole life.",
        "I miss you very much and I was over the moon when I read your message, that you're coming here on your honeymoon. So, I want to invite you to spend this time at my house. My house is your house. However, if you have another plan, I will understand it, because the honeymoon is a special time. But, I hope, that we could arrange a meeting, at least.",
        "Hope to see you soon,",
        "Lots of love,",
        "Bim"
